          "page_number": 3,
          "block_type": "text",
          "block_type_cn": "文本",
          "text_content": "1. Main Brand Category accounts for approximately \\(23\\%\\) ; 2. Digital Enterprises Category accounts for approximately \\(45\\%\\) (Leading Enterprises \\(13\\%\\) , Growth Value Enterprises \\(18\\%\\) , Mobile Marketing Enterprises \\(15\\%\\) ); 3. Digital Marketing Product Effectiveness Category accounts for approximately \\(1\\%\\) ; 4. Personality Category accounts for approximately \\(13\\%\\) ; 5. Media Category accounts for approximately \\(13\\%\\) .",
