          "text_content": "Based on the award application work, the enthusiasm of brands for digital marketing is increasing; the ecological expansion and innovative strength of digital companies continue to push forward; the development of Internet marketing products tends to combine product and effectiveness; the demand for scale and effect of Internet startups is increasingly obvious, reflected on the \"New Third Board\";",
