      "markdown_text": "=====================\n\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\n\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 100, 1280])\n\n=====================\n\nAt the start of the new year, everything is refreshed. On the first day back to work in the new year, the conference committee wishes all judges good health and smooth work.  \n\nFrom December 7th to December 31st, the award collection work for the conference has been successfully completed.  \n\nThe data from the award submissions show:  \n\n1. Main Brand Category accounts for approximately \\(23\\%\\) ;  \n\n2. Digital Enterprises Category accounts for approximately \\(45\\%\\) (Leading Enterprises \\(13\\%\\) , Growth Value Enterprises \\(18\\%\\) , Mobile Marketing Enterprises \\(15\\%\\) );  \n\n3. Digital Marketing Product Effectiveness Category accounts for approximately \\(1\\%\\) ;  \n\n4. Personality Category accounts for approximately \\(13\\%\\) ;  \n\n5. Media Category accounts for approximately \\(13\\%\\) .  \n\nBased on the award application work, the enthusiasm of brands for digital marketing is increasing; the ecological expansion and innovative strength of digital companies continue to push forward; the development of Internet marketing products tends to combine product and effectiveness; the demand for scale and effect of Internet startups is increasingly obvious, reflected on the \"New Third Board\";  \n\nThe strategy of media's digital transformation is particularly clear.  \n\nFrom January 4th to January 7th, please, respected reviewing judges, according to your professional experience, vote among the 8 categories of award candidates in the attachment as per the requirements.  \n\n(Your voting power accounts for \\(80\\%\\) , which will directly determine the final award winners)  \n\nThank you very much!  \n\n2016- 01- 04  \n\nDMCC (Digital Marketing Committee of China)"
